<h2>Know your username!</h2><p>This is the name you use when you log onto your machine when you first start up in the morning. When we know your username we can look up your account details more quickly to find any problems there.</p>
<h2>Detailed Information</h2>
<p>When you call the Help Desk, please give them your first and last name, phone number / email address a detailed description of the problem and another person to contact in case you are not in your office when CCOMM IT investigates the problem.</p>
